Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}星星總是充滿了魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}凶手常常也是演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}今天的事件稍有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}解開3個饒有趣味的詭計 體味解謎的快感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}外表看似小孩 頭腦却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.90,0:02:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你嘆什麽氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}不是 我只是擔心小蘭姐姐的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一定沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.80,0:02:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}畢竟做了那麽多練習 昨天還早早地睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}肯定輕而易舉地獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:17.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}不是都說過了嗎 我確實看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那個是夕月日式點心店的老闆娘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}應該是自殺啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}另一個是木下巡查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}請問出了什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}毛利先生 你來得正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 請聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.60,0:02:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 這可真讓我爲難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.30,0:02:40.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.40,0:02:47.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}又辣又苦的甜湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽先整理一下你們倆所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}老闆娘看見一個男子正想從這公寓1樓的105室逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}時間大約是兩小時前的早晨9點之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後木下巡查接到老闆娘的通知後就趕過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.70,0:03:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.70,0:03:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}然後就發現了租房人小澤文枝的尸體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}木下先生你就判定其爲自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}絕對不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:22.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}聽好了 我親眼看過現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死者服裝整潔 房間也幷不亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}而且也沒有其他目擊者看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:32.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你所說的那個可疑男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但是 我真的親眼看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.50,0:03:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}毛利先生 你來評評理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我希望能再徹底地調查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}那僞裝成自殺的可能性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:51.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爲了慎重起見 也請法醫調查了一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}根據尸體死後的僵硬程度來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:58.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}死亡時間推定爲昨晚6點到8點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果像這位老闆娘所說是那名男子所爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽他行凶後再僞裝成自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}這樣他就在房間裏和尸體一同待了13小時以上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是違背常識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你們是不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}讓毛利先生來判斷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}毛利先生 拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我真爲難呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.90,0:04:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我倒沒看出來你有爲難的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}木下先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}我所看到的男子就是這個人 絕對不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請不要亂碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死去的是住在這個房間的小澤文枝小姐 24歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}消費者金融公司的文員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我所看到的小澤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是穿著浴衣 脖子上套著鋼絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以靠著墻壁的坐姿死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即便是自殺也是選了個很奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 請您看這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}電腦裏留著遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}信貸部的清水主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}給您添麻煩了 我將以死來謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.00,0:05:28.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}遺書的內容是說挪用了公司3千多萬元的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此以死來謝罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}遺書是寫給上司的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是挪用公款啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}發送郵件的時間是昨天傍晚5點45分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我認爲就是在那之後死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}別搗亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}振動模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}明明是在家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:11.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看來情况確實像木下巡查所說是自殺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請看一下日曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不是預約要看牙醫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}日曆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}確實寫著今天預約了牙醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過老闆娘你的眼睛真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從那裏都能看到這些字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}連鋼絲都準備好了的有計劃的自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.80,0:06:42.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣的人會預約去看牙醫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.20,0:06:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}木下先生 這麽一來莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然還是他殺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}被照片上的那個男人所殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}這個還不能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}木下先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:07:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}你來這個房間的時候 房門是怎樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}房門沒上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.60,0:07:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}這麽說來 自殺時沒鎖門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.20,0:07:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從自殺者的心理來講應該避免中途被人發現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}門口的照片是從這裏取下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:22.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這個男的和死去的姐姐看上去很親密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但好像沒有給他留下遺書嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔 這是什麽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}像是沾著白色的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒有氣味又顆粒分明的粉末
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想這個粉末是能食用的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個大概是澱粉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}澱粉除了能做菜之外還能幹什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}還能做點心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:14.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}大福餅上面沾著的那個就是澱粉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:21.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 小澤小姐的公司少了3千萬元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.50,0:08:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且上司清水今天休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.30,0:08:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那看來他還不知道小澤小姐自殺了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且還發現了一件意外的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}照片上這個搬著便携式冷藏箱的男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就是遺書的收件人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}也就是那位清水主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}這麽說來上司就是戀人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}他們兩人交往的事公司裏沒有任何人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.00,0:08:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且這個叫清水的人喜歡賭博 花錢如流水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 這還真可疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}打擾一下 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}從房裏出來的就是他 你老實交代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}不好意思 你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}住手 請不要干擾辦案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k10}爲什麽 爲什麽要殺害她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}警官 這就是清水先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}他正在家休息 我們把他請過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我直說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.70,0:09:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你的部下小澤小姐挪用了3千萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這事你瞭解嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}不 我也是剛從警察那裏得知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是吃了一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.20,0:09:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你不是和小澤文枝小姐是戀人關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有什麽事都應該會互相商量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}竟說我們是戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}你是指警察手裏的那張照片是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}那是小澤她想去釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是陪她一起去而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}你今天早上9點之後在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}您爲什麽這麽問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}有人看到你從這裏跳下去想要逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}別裝傻 我看得清清楚楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我就不客氣地說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}你早上9點是不是來這裏殺了小澤文枝小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你是不是想說我利用了小澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.50,0:10:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}把公司的錢用完後就殺了她 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.00,0:10:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}就像吸吮完滿滿的甜湯後就拍屁股走人那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.80,0:10:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我昨天在廣島參加小學同學的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天早上9點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}我正在等候10點飛往羽田機場的航班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是票根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.40,0:10:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽你昨天晚上6點到8點在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那時同學會進行了一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}這是接待人員的名片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.50,0:10:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我們先借用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}請便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}請確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:01.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}清水先生有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但老闆娘却堅信自己沒看錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果這不是自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽樣 那個男的所說的都是謊話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}正如清水先生所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.80,0:11:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}和同學會的接待人以及航空公司都確認過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 老闆娘大概把誰和清水先生搞錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但老闆娘能看見那麽遠的日曆上的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}眼睛應該很好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}那犯人和清水很像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那麽 堀田那邊怎麽樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}他正在門口詢問送貨人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.30,0:12:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}看他們有沒有見到什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:13.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}看來我的不在場證明成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那我先行告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}你不能回去 這個人就是殺人凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}真是讓我爲難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}你是不是和我有什麽仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}你有證明我就是犯人的證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我是看著這個孩子長大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:42.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她還把我當母親一樣 什麽事都跟我講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}和叫清水的人交往的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}連同受他的指使挪用公司的錢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她都跟我坦白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}真不明白你在說些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真癢啊 快停下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要是沒有調到振動狀態就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}牙醫 我拜托您的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}小澤文枝小姐的牙都沒壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是她預約了牙醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}多謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.70,0:13:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}牙齒都沒問題却預約了牙醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個 容我說句多餘的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}日曆上的字和小澤的字迹不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.10,0:13:33.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是她的上司 有很多機會看到她的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.30,0:13:38.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這要鑒定後才能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但看來是不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那日曆上的字到底是誰寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.10,0:13:49.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看來第一發現者是老闆娘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.00,0:13:55.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}第一發現者往往也有可能是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果老闆娘是犯人的話那就遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這話什麽意思 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}老闆娘爲了讓清水先生看上去像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.10,0:14:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以讓人以爲小澤小姐預約了牙醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.50,0:14:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且昨晚還把照片取出來放在醒目的大門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}麻煩你寫一下"預約了牙醫"這幾個字好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你確定是這位女士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}藏在這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.10,0:14:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}老闆娘 你早上9點後來過這個房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.90,0:14:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}送貨司機看到你從這個房間跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且你顯得很著急幷和司機撞上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有5百萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}這些錢是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}爲什麽藏在燃氣箱裏 能請你解釋一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}錢是我從家裏帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}藏起來是因爲發現了文枝的尸體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怕萬一去警察局報警時弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我這樣想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}果然你還是進了這個房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.00,0:15:32.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你自己殺害了小澤小姐 却要嫁禍給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你在說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.80,0:15:37.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}毛利先生 請不要相信這個男人所說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是爲難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}說謊 有一個人在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到底誰是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}魚的鱗片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}爲什麽會在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是這樣啊 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:16.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我寫的 門口的照片也是我弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是爲了讓清水先生來頂罪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}是爲了想讓你們逮捕犯人清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}我今天早上來過這房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.40,0:16:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我想把它給準備自首的文枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想多少還上一點錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}或許罪行就能减輕一些 所以我凑了些錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:45.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我看到了完全變了個樣的文枝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}直覺告訴我這都是清水做的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}她說過要對警察坦白一切的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:56.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可由于這房間中絲毫沒有清水先生行凶的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.70,0:17:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}于是你就在門口放置了照片 日曆上也做了手脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人就是站在這裏的清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}這些全都是你的一面之詞 不能完全采信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因爲清水先生他是有不在場證明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}我很想知道您是從哪里凑到5百萬的巨款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}能請您說明一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生 讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.70,0:17:31.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}這位是制冰店的井上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.60,0:17:34.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}制冰店 這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}正如毛利先生您推測的一樣 他買過冰塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}佐藤 崛田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}先把她帶回警署進行詢問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 請您等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.90,0:18:03.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}毛利 要開始了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.10,0:18:10.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}請您立刻放了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.20,0:18:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}該跟警察走的是清水先生你才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爲什麽我要跟警察走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.70,0:18:20.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}井上先生 這個人是什麽時候去買冰塊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.90,0:18:25.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昨天中午 買了4大塊冰共10千克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我記得他還準備了一個很大的冷藏箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽現在這季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}冰塊融化消失需要多長時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.60,0:18:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}常溫的話需要半天左右吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}百忙之中勞您前來 十分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.30,0:18:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}多謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}佐藤刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:53.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}澡盆蓋底下有些魚的鱗片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有 請你把鐵絲取下拿過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}浴室裏有魚的鱗片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}清水先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}在昨天的中午時分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你應該是下了安眠藥使文枝小姐昏睡過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}再把她架到了浴室裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.40,0:19:12.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}然後讓她坐在用冰塊和澡盆蓋搭成的椅子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}隨著冰塊融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}脖子就會被勒住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}在死亡推測時間的晚上6點到8點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}冰塊已經只剩一半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.00,0:19:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}可是當今天早上老闆娘發現的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}冰塊已經完全融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}而且浴室地上的水也已經幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.70,0:19:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概是放在搬運冰塊的冷藏箱裏的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.20,0:19:36.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}澡盆蓋上沾著了魚的鱗片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此 這就成了我殺人的證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}小澤在傍晚5點45分的時候還給我發過郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果真是那樣被鐵絲勒住脖子而不省人事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她又怎樣給我發遺書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.80,0:19:55.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}柯南 把小澤的手機放到書架的空位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把一部分懸空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}手機處于振動模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}佐藤刑警 請你打個電話到小澤小姐的手機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看一下手機的通話記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.60,0:20:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}在傍晚5點45分前不久應該有來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.30,0:20:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 這幷不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.20,0:20:36.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我當時可是在廣島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}真是不見棺材不落泪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}佐藤刑警 請你看看鐵絲上的那個結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.20,0:20:46.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}上邊纏著頭髮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}除了小澤小姐那染過色的頭髮外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}還有沒有其它的毛髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.10,0:20:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}有根黑而直的類似頭髮的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:55.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}清水先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}在你把小澤小姐架起來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:21:02.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}你的頭髮纏到了小澤小姐的頭髮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而你却沒有注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}清水先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.50,0:21:08.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}只要一鑒定 這是誰的頭髮就一清二楚了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}實在對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:20.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}她說再也忍不下去 要找警察自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你吸吮了不少甜湯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}今後 你就好好嘗嘗自己煲的苦味湯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.40,0:23:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是太精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}毛利先生 目暮警官全告訴我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.50,0:23:43.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}那真是一場讓清水自食苦果的精彩戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.70,0:23:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}據說要嘗出甜味來 先要放點鹽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.40,0:23:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也想來點鹽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}黃金周劇場版新作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}名偵探柯南 水平綫上的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.90,0:24:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}有史以來最大的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}沈睡小五郎的推理最終能否照亮真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還沒有欣賞的你 現在就趕快到電影院去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.90,0:24:17.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是20年前的那個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這不是小蘭打來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}也就是說 莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.00,0:24:24.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.20,0:24:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}奇怪一家的委托（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.60,0:24:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}手機的鎖定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}對了 高木刑警呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.00,0:24:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}因爲今天的標題是甜湯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.60,0:24:54.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}佐藤
